      "role": "user",
      "content": "i feel like im just stuck in this same shitty cycle forever. every time i think i finally figured things out or got a stable job or met someone good, it just falls apart. it's like i'm wired to fail and nothing i do actually changes the outcome. im just exhausted from trying to fix something that isnt fixable.",
